OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FMinutes from a meeting between Swansea
OL,8,FCouncil and the Welsh Rugby Union show
OL,9,Fthe council was told the Ospreys, one
OL,10,Fof Wales' four professional rugby
OL,11,Fregions, would cease operating as a
OL,12,Fmen's team next year.
OL,14,FThe document appears to directly
OL,15,Fcontradict comments made by WRU senior
OL,16,Fofficials that no decision had been
OL,17,Ftaken about which team might disappear
OL,18,Fas part of plans to cut the number of
OL,19,Fprofessional sides in Wales from four
OL,20,Fto three.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
