FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FThe council says the January meeting
OL,8,Fmade it "absolutely clear" the Ospreys
OL,9,Fwould no longer exist if the WRU's
OL,10,Fproposed investment in Cardiff Rugby
OL,11,Fwent ahead.
OL,13,FThe WRU has called that claim
OL,14,F"inaccurate".
OL,16,FLast month its chair, Richard Collier-
OL,17,FKeywood, told a Senedd committee the
OL,18,F"assumption" that the Ospreys would be
OL,19,Fthe club killed off "was not the case".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FThis week, the union's chief
OL,8,Fexecutive, Abi Tierney, said the board
OL,9,F"hadn't made a decision".
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FHowever, the bombshell minutes, seen
OL,17,Fby ITV News, make clear that Swansea
OL,18,Fwould lose its professional regional
OL,19,Fteam at St Helens if the proposed deal
OL,20,Fwith Y11 goes ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FThe minutes were later sent to Abi
OL,8,FTierney and include her handwritten
OL,9,Fannotations in red. She challenges
OL,10,Fsome of the wording in the document,
OL,11,Fbut does not dispute the section
OL,12,Frecording that professional men's
OL,13,Frugby would no longer be played at St
OL,14,FHelens if the Cardiff sale went ahead.
OL,16,FThe minutes suggest that internally
OL,17,Fthe WRU were already working on the
OL,18,Fassumption that the Ospreys would
OL,19,Fdisappear in the scenario that Y11
OL,20,Fbought Cardiff.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
