PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FThe minutes have been revealed after
OL,8,Fthe WRU submitted a Freedom of
OL,9,FInformation request to Swansea
OL,10,FCouncil. The union had previously
OL,11,Ftried to prevent their release.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News, Swansea Council
OL,14,Fleader Rob Stewart said Abi Tierney
OL,15,Fshould now resign, Mr Stewart has
OL,16,Falready called for the WRU chair
OL,17,FRichard Collier-Keywood to step down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,F"Our statements are vindicated by the
OL,8,Frelease of the minutes which prove
OL,9,Fbeyond doubt what we had said is true,
OL,10,Fand reinforce our need to take legal
OL,11,Faction against the WRU.
OL,13,F"Having pressured Swansea Council to
OL,14,Fkeep the minutes confidential, Ms
OL,15,FTierney then submitted a freedom of
OL,16,Finformation request, which the council
OL,17,Fhas now responded to."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,F"Ms Tierney may not have realised that
OL,8,Fin submitting the FOI, she has made
OL,9,Fthe information that the WRU were
OL,10,Ftrying to keep private - public!"
OL,12,F"It's now really clear the actions
OL,13,Fwere duplicitous, the statements
OL,14,Fmisleading, the processes
OL,15,Fpredetermined, and what little trust
OL,16,Fremained has now been completely
OL,17,Fdestroyed. Ms Tierney must now resign
OL,18,Fimmediately to restore trust in Welsh
OL,19,Frugby."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
