OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773529872
OL,3,CWRU comments on Ospreys future
OL,4,Cchallenged by newly-released meeting
OL,5,Cminutes
OL,7,FThe leader also claims the report
OL,8,F"raises questions" over whether the
OL,9,Fchair of the WRU "misled the Senedd
OL,10,Fcommittee" in recent evidence.
OL,12,F"The board now need to clarify if they
OL,13,Fhave participated in creating and
OL,14,Fmaking the misleading statements, and
OL,15,Fwhether they were aware of Ms
OL,16,FTierney's actions."
OL,18,FThe WRU have been contacted for
OL,19,Fcomment.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]qD@ROUrD@JO]
